      IRB processes for low or minimal risk research. The IRB is undergoing review by the Business Process Improvement unit at the University with the goal of making the process more efficient.
    </p>
    
  </div>

</article>                          <article class="tease tease-news" id="tease-369">
	
  
  <div class="teaser-content">
    <h2 class="_title"><a href="https://provost.uic.edu/news-stories/length-time-legal-review-research-contracts/">Length of time for legal review of research contracts</a></h2>

              <div class="post-meta">
    <div class="post-date-line">
            <span class="post-date">Posted on <strong>October 31, 2016</strong></span>
    </div>
    </div>
        
        <p>
      The legal review of research contracts takes too long, and sometimes it takes so long that funding is lost. The Office of Research Services (ORS) in the Office of the Vice Chancellor for&hellip;
    </p>
    
  </div>

</article>                          <article class="tease tease-news" id="tease-367">
	
  
  <div class="teaser-content">
    <h2 class="_title"><a href="https://provost.uic.edu/news-stories/paying-international-scholars/">Paying international scholars</a></h2>

              <div class="post-meta">
    <div class="post-date-line">
            <span class="post-date">Posted on <strong>October 31, 2016</strong></span>
    </div>
    </div>
        
        <p>
      Several people reported difficulty in bringing in and paying international scholars who are invited to UIC by our faculty. We are investigating this issue.
    </p>
    
  </div>

</article>                          <article class="tease tease-news" id="tease-365">
	
  
  <div class="teaser-content">
    <h2 class="_title"><a href="https://provost.uic.edu/news-stories/procurement-system-problems/">Procurement system problems</a></h2>

              <div class="post-meta">
    <div class="post-date-line">
            <span class="post-date">Posted on <strong>October 31, 2016</strong></span>
    </div>
    </div>
        
        <p>
      There were reports of problems arising out of the procurement system. These are under review.
    </p>
    
  </div>

</article>                          <article class="tease tease-news" id="tease-363">
	
  
  <div class="teaser-content">
    <h2 class="_title"><a href="https://provost.uic.edu/news-stories/charging-workshops-continuing-education-services-provided-outside-constituents/">Charging for workshops and continuing education and other services provided to outside constituents</a></h2>

